{{--
    Process-timeline ghost numeral as an inline SVG.

    Why SVG and not text: the ghosts are stroke-only, and Unbounded (a variable
    font) builds its digits from overlapping path components — -webkit-text-stroke
    traces every component's outline, so the internal construction seams show
    (e.g. a small "1"-shaped stem inside the "5"). These paths are the same
    Unbounded glyphs (wght 600) with the overlaps boolean-unioned away via
    fontTools + skia-pathops — one clean contour per digit, no seams.

    Param: $n (1-7). Styling (stroke/fill/glow) lives in marketing.css.
--}}
